OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776409519
OL,3,CPassengers told 'do not travel' to
OL,4,Cmajor station after overhead wires
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FPassengers travelling to and from
OL,8,FManchester Piccadilly are facing
OL,9,F"major disruptions" due to an overhead
OL,10,Fwire fault.
OL,12,FAll trains running through the major
OL,13,Fstation are facing hour-long delays or
OL,14,Fhave been cancelled entirely, with
OL,15,Foperators telling passengers not to
OL,16,Ftravel to Piccadilly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
