PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776409519
OL,3,CPassengers told 'do not travel' to
OL,4,Cmajor station after overhead wires
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FOperators affected by the issue
OL,8,Finclude Avanti West Coast,
OL,9,FCrossCountry, East Midlands Railway,
OL,10,FNorthern, TransPennine Express and
OL,11,FTransport for Wales. A Network Rail
OL,12,Fteam is "heading to the site" and the
OL,13,Fdisruption is expected until the end
OL,14,Fof the day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
