FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776409519
OL,3,CPassengers told 'do not travel' to
OL,4,Cmajor station after overhead wires
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,FNational Rail said: "Damage to the
OL,8,Foverhead electric wires at Manchester
OL,9,FPiccadilly means that some lines are
OL,10,Fblocked. As a result, trains running
OL,11,Fto / from this station may be
OL,12,Fcancelled or severely delayed by up to
OL,13,F60 minutes. Major disruption is
OL,14,Fexpected until the end of the day."
OL,16,FAnd Northern has told passengers not
OL,17,Fto travel to Piccadilly. A post says:
OL,18,F"Due to overhead wire damage just
OL,19,Foutside Manchester Piccadilly, we are
OL,20,Fadvising people not to travel to /
OL,21,Ffrom the station at this time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
