PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776409519
OL,3,CPassengers told 'do not travel' to
OL,4,Cmajor station after overhead wires
OL,5,Cfault
OL,7,F"Train services across south
OL,8,FManchester that run into Piccadilly
OL,9,Fwill be cancelled or amended at short
OL,10,Fnotice."
OL,12,FA Piccadilly spokesperson added:
OL,13,F"We're investigating an issue in the
OL,14,Farea. Sorry for any disruption to your
OL,15,Fjourney."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
